# Janus Io raw experiment logs and proof archives can be large and may contain
# local paths or operational identifiers. Commit them intentionally with
# `git add -f` only after sanitization and review. Existing tracked evidence
# remains tracked until it is deliberately moved into a curated proof pack.
janus_io_o1_runs/**/*.log
janus_io_o1_runs/**/raw_log.txt
janus_io_o1_runs/**/proofs/
janus_io_o1_runs/**/*.tmp.*
